{"tid":255653,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"依家d 90後見到9:15AM先紅雨就屌哂鬼，醜態盡現！","createTime":"2017-05-24T03:51:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T04:05:49.000Z","uid":294,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5f3e1c5bf33fc77ccbccae4e4aac5c6639c40500","tid":255653,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T03:51:00.000Z","msg":"我地公司返9AM，<br />\n<br />\n有隻90後已經遲左成3分鐘，賴黃雨。<br />\n<br />\n支支整整搞左10幾分鐘都未正式開工，佢突然大叫：<br />\n<br />\n「屌依家先紅雨！台長早多幾個字洗死咩」<br />\n<br />\n第一，<br />\n<br />\n返工係唔比用電話，你偷睇Notification就已經唔岩，<br />\n<br />\n第二，<br />\n<br />\n人地天文台有既定程序架啦，<br />\n<br />\n台長做野洗你教？<br />\n<br />\n咁叻你就唔洗做倉啦。有咩資格去評論人地？<br />\n<br />\n醜態盡現！<br />\n<br />\n一陣我一定同呀Head講，篤佢背脊，嘻"},{"pid":"b45c1d7b017ce3d77bc73d9458ab404e33a3d93a","tid":255653,"uid":7954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T03:52:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b46dde2d9739dee0c8e83998f2d8115d6a84781d","tid":255653,"uid":56634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T03:53:28.000Z","msg":"紅雨都要番工<br />\n零分重作"},{"pid":"c3782088e0d894a1f718abbdf833276e6aa66cd1","tid":255653,"uid":35712,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T03:53:48.000Z","msg":"黑雨啦 打幾隻字 九點打到而加 唔怪之得d野要比哂d細做啦靠你班老屎忽 打份文件都要兩日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79b671733fd8a400809f7cd412363f24b97e3fe4","tid":255653,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T03:55:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>紅雨都要番工<br />\n零分重作</blockquote><br />\n紅雨我地做戶外唔洗返"},{"pid":"7f0ffefe7d986468482ff1bb0afc8e11c0dae441","tid":255653,"uid":96473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T03:56:05.000Z","msg":"垃圾都上熱門 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"